{
  "id": "tpl_demo_apidocs_001",
  "name": "api_docs_generation",
  "display_name": "API 文档自动生成",
  "description": "演示 API 文档生成技能，自动分析代码接口并生成标准 API 文档",
  "icon": "📖",
  "category": "ai-workflow",
  "subcategory": "development",
  "tags": ["api", "docs", "documentation", "openapi", "demo", "skill"],
  "project_type": "workflow",
  "prompt_template": "请帮我自动生成 API 文档：\n\n**项目路径：** {{projectPath}}\n**文档格式：** {{docFormat}}\n**API 框架：** {{framework}}\n\n**生成步骤：**\n\n### 步骤1：扫描 API 端点\n```\n/api-docs-generator scan {{projectPath}} --framework {{framework}}\n```\n\n### 步骤2：生成文档\n```\n/api-docs-generator generate {{projectPath}} --format {{docFormat}}\n```\n\n### 步骤3：代码审查\n```\n/code-review {{projectPath}}\n```\n\n### 步骤4：保存结果\n```\n/memory-management save \"API文档生成: {{projectPath}}\"\n```\n\n**使用的技能：** api-docs-generator, code-review, memory-management",
  "variables_schema": [
    {
      "name": "projectPath",
      "label": "项目路径",
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "placeholder": "src/api/ 或 backend/routes/"
    },
    {
      "name": "docFormat",
      "label": "文档格式",
      "type": "select",
      "required": true,
      "options": [
        { "value": "openapi", "label": "OpenAPI/Swagger" },
        { "value": "markdown", "label": "Markdown" },
        { "value": "html", "label": "HTML" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "framework",
      "label": "API 框架",
      "type": "select",
      "required": false,
      "default": "auto",
      "options": [
        { "value": "auto", "label": "自动检测" },
        { "value": "express", "label": "Express.js" },
        { "value": "fastapi", "label": "FastAPI" },
        { "value": "springboot", "label": "Spring Boot" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "file_structure": {},
  "default_files": [],
  "is_builtin": true,
  "author": "ChainlessChain Team",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "usage_count": 0,
  "rating": 0,
  "rating_count": 0,
  "skills_used": ["api-docs-generator", "code-review", "memory-management"],
  "difficulty": "intermediate",
  "execution_engine": "skill"
}
